Name:           perl-Config-Any
Summary:        Load configuration from different file formats, transparently
Version:        0.33
Release:        6%{?dist}
License:        GPL-1.0-or-later OR Artistic-1.0-Perl
URL:            https://metacpan.org/release/Config-Any
